Description:
Welcome to Spud's Creative Asylum. 
This bath caddy is perfect for relaxing in the bubbles, with a good book, a glass of wine and some ambient lighting. It can also be used for holding a tablet or smart phone. We have iPads, iPhones and a Samsung smart phone and the integrated steel holder accommodates all of those. 
The book / tablet holder is made from sturdy steel rebar and this is fitted securely into the shelf. The shelf itself is made from reclaimed wood and coated in Danish oil to protect from steam and water and keep this looking beautiful. 
There is plenty of room to hold a bottle of wine and maybe your favourite chocolates. These make perfect gifts. 
Because I use reclaimed wood, every piece will have it's own history, marks, grooves and cuts. Please note that due to the natural markings and grain in the wood, the depth of colour may differ between each one. 
This fits a standard size 700mm wide bath, but I'm happy to make this in various sizes if required. Anti slip rubber feet are also fixed to the bottom of each shelf to stop them sliding.
I can make several variations to this design:
*One wine glass slot 
*One wine glass slot and one wine bottle/ mug / pint glass recess
*Two wine glass slots
*Pint glass / mug recess
Regardless of the design above, each one will still come fitted with the metal book / tablet stand.
This product is made to order, from selecting the wood, cutting, sanding, assembling and finishing. A lot of time, love and care goes into each piece and this is reflected in the quality of the finished product.  
Accessories not included.

Product name: Kids Behaviour Reward Chart, toddler routine chart, visual aid, ASD, ADHD, kids magnet reward chart, full imagery, picture reward chart
Description:
Here we have a fully magnetized, fully personalised, fully customisable reward chart for the little angel in your life! This chart is the perfect visual aid for those pre-school children, toddlers or children with SEN, ASD, ADHD, GDD or need that visual aid as oppose to wording on their charts.
How does this work, 
Every day your child has 15 jobs, behaviours or routines they need to adhere to. If they complete their task for the day they would get their magnet to fill the circle. 
You would let your child know how well they are doing so far with the coloured faces. 
Red sad face - not doing so well
Orange neutral face - try harder
Green happy face - brilliant day! 
Whatever face the day ends on would move over to the weekly section on the chart. 
You will see there is a space for their magnet treat of the week. These are also pictures, if they worked hard enough throughout the week they would get their treat (mums discretion of course!)  
The magnets come in any colour and are sparkly. Please do let me know if your child doesn't want glitter 
These charts can be edited at a later date and as a result can grow with the child. Feel free to contact me at a later stage to create a new insert. Or you can find the listing to get your personalised finished chart sent over to your PC in a file here 
https://www.etsy.com/your/shops/OliHarriCreations/tools/listings/240297601
 With this file, your chart can be adapted as many times as you need to 
If this wasn't quite what you were looking for I do offer a variety of Reward chart options which can all be found here 
https://www.etsy.com/shop/OliHarriCreations?section_id=16807316&ref=shopsection_leftnav_6
  Any questions, ideas or adaptations you would like to make feel free to send me a message. 
In order to create your perfect chart I will send you an email with all the information I need from you and you can fill it out at your leisure. And that's it.

Product name: Bucket List - Travel Journal - 4.5 x 6 inch A6 - Bucket List Journal
Description:
Bucket list journal! A place to list the things you want to do, or record the things you have done.
A6 mixed paper travel journal with a black faux leather soft cover. The inside cover is hand painted with a white and purple checkered design. The small size is perfect for travelling and journaling on the move.  
Over 80 pages of assorted paper. The majority of the pages are unlined and neutral in colour (white, off-white) but vary in texture and weight. I have also included some pink and purple paper to match the colour theme of the book.
You will also find some of these papers added, some full sized pages, some half sized pages, and some smaller additions:
- lined/ruled (vertical and horizontal)
- squared
- manuscript paper (unused music paper)
- textured
- salvaged paper (from reused envelopes)
- recycled elephant poo paper
- recycled bank note paper
- recycled banana paper
- practice writing paper
- cash book paper
- tracing paper
- graph paper
The great variety of paper is what I find most fun about this book. I like to have a different combination of papers each time you turn a page. Some pages are small or torn in half. There's an envelope sewn into one of the signatures (pictured) so you can keep things inside there. There's also a 'mini book' sewn into one of the signatures (pictured).

Description:
A simple natural, healing stone pendant with a raw Jadeite (Imperial Jade) mineral stone. It can be worn over the throat or heart chakra, for both men and women.
**NB: These stones have some uneven sharp points so are not recommended for use by children.
******************************
How did we make it?
* With a technique known as micro MACRAMÉ - the art of tying knots 
* Using materials sourced on our travels: 
Waxed thread - an incredibly strong, washable, colour-fast thread 
Green Jade (Jadeite) stone - approximate sizes available are:  /-2cms, /-2.5cms, /-3cms, /-3.5, /-4cms, /-4.5cms, /-5cms
****************************** 
What else do you need to know?
The necklace may vary slightly from the one in the picture. All our stones are a lovely, green colour but do let us know if you'd like to see the actual one which will be yours before you purchase and we'll be happy to send you photos.
* Each stone varies slightly in size between 2cms to 5cms
* Adjustable cord length - maximum length 82cms (32")
* Slide system close - very secure (and easy to do on your own!)
* No metal used at all so hypo-allergenic
* All our items are sent out in eco-friendly, up-cycled/recycled packaging wherever possible

What properties does the stone have?
